title: Sales by Product
filter_row_source: SELECT DISTINCT [Product Name] FROM [`dl_northwind`.`products`] ORDER BY [Product Name];

title: Sales By Customer
filter_row_source: SELECT DISTINCT [Company] FROM [customers Extended] ORDER BY [Company];

title: Sales By Employee
filter_row_source: SELECT DISTINCT [Employee Name] FROM [`dl_northwind`.`employees` Extended] ORDER BY [Employee Name];

title: Sales By Country
filter_row_source: SELECT DISTINCT [country_region] FROM [customers Extended] ORDER BY [country_region];
